/* effective AC is screwy.  use item: worn and set armor with affect flags */
A multiplier to effective armor is applied according to body location.
All multipliers are 1, except head and body which are 2.  Hence, 15 acapply
shield reduces armor 15 points.  15 acapply platemail reduces armor 30 points.

Monk's are unable to wear this type of item at all.


